you hear about this nonstop.

00:50:14.840 --> 00:50:15.910
So I'm curious--

00:50:15.910 --> 00:50:16.330
LEE ALLEN DUGATKIN: Oh, really?

00:50:16.330 --> 00:50:17.775
You hear about this experiment?

00:50:17.775 --> 00:50:18.300
AUDIENCE: Oh, yeah.

00:50:18.300 --> 00:50:18.670
LEE ALLEN DUGATKIN: Oh, good.

00:50:18.670 --> 00:50:19.714
That's good to know.

00:50:19.714 --> 00:50:21.490
AUDIENCE: It's part of the
