OK.

00:53:29.720 --> 00:53:30.447
OK, yeah, sure.

00:53:30.447 --> 00:53:32.280
AUDIENCE: First of all,
thanks for the talk.

00:53:32.280 --> 00:53:33.240
LEE ALLEN DUGATKIN:
You're welcome.

00:53:33.240 --> 00:53:34.410
AUDIENCE: I was
wondering, in your words,

00:53:34.410 --> 00:53:36.840
you said that this happened
